  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We won't have any bread today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, children, they did not know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just were worried that they won't have bread, still we were not gonna bake.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father said to me then-- like-- he said-- he called me by the Jewish name, [INAUDIBLE]-- put it down, we won't need it anymore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what he said to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went in, and I don't even remember what happened to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To this day, I feel-- I went in kind of like-- they call it-- like-- a lump in the stomach, kind of like just press thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Would you believe it, it never went away, even now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All right, I am happy, when the happy times are, you know, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't say that I am always, that I'm-- you know, because life goes on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm happy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think about any little thing, any little thought of home, any little thought of whatever, it's there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It never went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So when that-- everybody start already getting prepared, [INAUDIBLE] the first thing is knapsacks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Everybody had suitcases, and we had our suitcases anyway but that's not-- you know, everybody I could take-- I don't remember how it was, if the sheriff came to say or what, I really don't, but us Jews, between ourselves, everybody start running to each other and giving ideas what we gonna do, what to do.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, the first thing, we didn't know when exactly they gonna come to our village so we-- and as I said, we had the-- the chickens, you know, and the [INAUDIBLE] was in the other side.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not like [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Polyana ?] was up towards one side and [INAUDIBLE] was in the other side, there was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
